{"tid":1718892,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【TVB台慶 = 幸災樂禍】每日洗版任務 - 致癌嘅 \"普利膚軟膏\"","createTime":"2019-11-14T03:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T23:26:54.000Z","uid":267969,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"3f13dccd72a42453f8aa08644b01b2d7ae84847e","tid":1718892,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:14:03.000Z","msg":"5個月以嚟，香港魔警肆虐，連醫院、學校都淪陷，香港人個個心痛至極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>但TVB同佢旗下偽人仲係平行時空綵排緊台慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n完全唔知香港人有幾難過架！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTVB將《萬千星輝賀台慶》改左做《珍惜香港，發放娛樂，TVB 52年》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n「為香港打氣」，好心TVB啦，真係關心香港既就報返啲真新聞、取消台慶啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇人有心情睇你台慶啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">行動預告：<br />\n11月19日晚將有大型鍵戰活動</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請各位戰士準備</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌每日只開一個抵制TVB行動post，唔會開9up post，<span style=\"color: red;\">請follow我個acc</span>、推post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【抵制CCTVB 每日任務】</span></strong></span><br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">推post</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n5. tag 多幾個friend做任 <br />\n <br />\n是日精選@14 Nov 2019 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>普利膚</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Lonadermcream/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLonadermcream%2F&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=fb39b35d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Lonadermcream/</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>※記得用留言template</strong></span></span><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">留言重點</span></strong>係全力阻止廣告商簽訂下年合約</strong> <br />\n<blockquote>無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/75204432_496983287825192_724212433354227712_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_eui2=AeG_YvcH7UDiBbRmiYMwxNocMbO2jg-aiTVTVdeXaxvhwfqr9MinfDgnUF2KMkSRw1tYstRb7bB7_bbg3GcFSuL38wPhZYI2WYsE0CXUUF0_sw&amp;_nc_oc=AQniEVlKfjUe52I2kAz6wbVOD7jDpyU-5BVcn4GcFTWjeoGAk7J-q-NZM4eIed_APkA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=9227996d9ee36369c8fed666c771e708&amp;oe=5E5A2633\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F75204432_496983287825192_724212433354227712_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_eui2%3DAeG_YvcH7UDiBbRmiYMwxNocMbO2jg-aiTVTVdeXaxvhwfqr9MinfDgnUF2KMkSRw1tYstRb7bB7_bbg3GcFSuL38wPhZYI2WYsE0CXUUF0_sw%26_nc_oc%3DAQniEVlKfjUe52I2kAz6wbVOD7jDpyU-5BVcn4GcFTWjeoGAk7J-q-NZM4eIed_APkA%26_nc_